# CODEOWNERS — who must review changes to matching paths.
#
# Owners are auto-requested for review on any PR that touches a matching
# path. This only *enforces* review if the branch ruleset has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled (Settings -> Rules -> Rulesets).
# Later matches win, so put the most specific rules last.
#
# Owners must be GitHub users/teams with write access to this repo.
# Replace @apesconsole below if you want a different handle or a team
# (e.g. @apesconsole/maintainers).

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                       @apesconsole

# Deploy pipeline and CI — changes here can affect the live site.
/.github/                @apesconsole
/.github/workflows/      @apesconsole

# Core site files.
/index.html              @apesconsole
/app.js                  @apesconsole
/styles.css              @apesconsole

# SEO / crawler surface.
/robots.txt              @apesconsole
/sitemap.xml             @apesconsole
